name: Humble Me
comments: What a great song - what a great voice!
This is my favorite song she does.  it is just so beautiful.
it never rains when you want it to...
truth spoke in whispers will tear you apart......indeed. it never rains when you want it to.
such a beautiful voice and woman.

Nossa, tem voz e ritmo que se encaixam
com uma perfeição...parece mesmo que 
nasceu pra aquele ritmo. coisa de Deus.
Ela é sempre maravilhosa e inspiradora!
Such a powerful song. Comparable to hallelujah. One of her best.
This is the best and most beautiful song she sings.  It is so wonderful.
this makes me feel really humble.... such beautiful voice
